<p><i><b>The Iciest Sin</b></i> is a crime novel by <a href="/wiki/H._R._F._Keating" title="H. R. F. Keating">H. R. F. Keating</a>. It is the eighteenth novel in the <a href="/wiki/Inspector_Ghote" title="Inspector Ghote">Inspector Ghote</a> series but the nineteenth book to be published as an anthology of short stories was released the year before.</p>
<p></p>
